      "rationale": "Three structured hexahedral meshes (2.1 M, 5.8 M, 14.4 M cells) were generated with uniform refinement ratio r = 1.38. Richardson extrapolation yields GCI_fine = 2.7% for RHI at the worst-case 2400 RPM / 4 L/min operating point. All other operating points exhibit GCI < 3.5%. Discretization error is adequately controlled."
