      "rationale": "RHI predictions agree within ±15% of measured values across all 5 operating points (mean error 8.3%). Pressure-head predictions agree within ±5% across the H-Q curve. Formal validation metric (ASME V&V 20 E_val) computed and reported in the validation report appendix. Achieved level 3 reflects quantitative uncertainty-aware comparison."
