    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates adequate predictive accuracy for RHI across the COU operating envelope. Discretization error is controlled (GCI < 5%), validation agreement is within ±15%, and the QoI used in validation is identical to the regulatory decision metric. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device submission.",
